snippet.title: Urban Legend Hunters 2: Double - Official Release Window Trailer
snippet.description: Meet the characters, see various locations, and more in this trailer for Urban Legend Hunters 2: Double, an upcoming visual novel adventure game based around urban legends. In this realistic thriller game, you get caught up in a mysterious incident in which the virtual world and reality intertwine. Urban Legend Hunters 2: Double will be available in Spring 2024 on Steam, Android, and iOS.
